    <li>Creativity</li>
    <li>Dynamism.</li>
    <li>Availability</li>
    <li>Adaptability</li>
    <li>Flexibility</li>
    <li>Ability to work in a team and independently</li>
    <li>Capacity for collaboration and commitment</li>
    <li>Orientation to achieve results</li>
    
    
  </ul>
</BaseLayout>
